            "title": "Welfare of pigs from birth to slaughter",
            "abstract": [
                "References -- Chapter 11.  The welfare of pigs: a social, ethical and scientific issue -- D. Fraser -- Abstract -- 1. Introduction -- 2. Debate about animal welfare -- 3. Animal welfare science -- 4. Animal welfare assurance programs -- 5. The application of animal welfare science -- References -- Index",
